<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَالَّذِي يُقَدَّرُ بِاللَّامِ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> غُلَامُ زَيْدٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالَّذِي يُقَدَّرُ بِمِنْ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> ثَوْبُ خَزٍّ، وَبَابُ سَاجٍ، وَخَاتَمُ حَدِيدٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَمَّ بِحَمْدِ اللهِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>